{
  "stem": "2522.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you were still subject to all the other restrictions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only thing the white card did is you were not deported.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went back to school because the head of the school was a friend of my father's, and it was a special accommodation.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he found-- he found a loophole in the law by which said well, you know, if he is baptized he doesn't fall into this category.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In other words, you don't have to fill a form which says Jew, but you could say, he's a Lutheran, you know, then, then you complied with the law.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You must understand this continual legalistic manipulation that takes place though all of this time, looking at the fine details of how to negotiate your way around this or that restriction.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Totally ended.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I must say that the conditions were so depressed and so extreme-- and by the way, then we had to move again, even after the baptism to a slum, to a really slum.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we were really pushed down into the gutter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That-- And the scrounging for food and, you know, scrounging for survival was so extreme that the luxury of anything else, even with the possibility of any kind of a betrayal seeing, for instance, lighting the candles on Friday night, just was totally out of question.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, the tenseness to protect yourself against possible accusation-- there was enough accusation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well these Jews just did it for, for the perform-- they're really not Lutherans, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was so intense that there was no Jewish life, so far as I remember it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No way.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, there was war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is 1942, '43, you know, the height of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so the idea of leaving was totally out of question.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
